output.name: GlassLensWatch
output.description: GlassLensWatch is an independent, nonprofit newsroom dedicated to producing investigative journalism that serves the public interest. With a team of over 100 committed journalists, the organization focuses on impactful stories that shed light on crucial issues and facilitate real-world change. They prioritize diversity and inclusivity within their newsroom and are committed to enhancing their workforce representation.
